headline: HP, Dell earnings: How AI is impacting the PC market
summary: Wall Street is preparing for quarterly earnings reports from HP (HPQ) and Dell (DELL), which will be released on Tuesday. Investors are interested in how the ongoing artificial intelligence revolution is impacting the personal computer market. Catalysts Co-hosts Seana Smith and Madison Mills break down market expectations surrounding these critical earnings releases as investors gauge how traditional PC manufacturers are positioning themselves to capitalize on widespread AI adoption. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Catalysts here. This post was written by Angel Smith
